Reduce toughness of Town Hall

commit.message:
Reduce toughness of Town Hall

remove native armor from all buildings (as in vanilla)
reduce town hall  HP to 1500 (from 2500).

why:
-it takes forever to take down TH (campaign also is boring for longer after finishing AI)
- lumber mill building armor upgrades become interesting investement
- 1500 hp value is tested for decades in W2.
- AI raids with few grunts/footman are more deadly to player
- it keeps the whole expansion economy more in check
